For all order types and size for equities priced below $1.00, regardless of shares traded in a given day, month, year, etc., or any other negotiated qualifier, Cobra Trading pays LAMP $0.05 per 100 shares. For all order types and size for equities priced above $1.00, regardless of shares traded in a given day, month, year, etc., or any other negotiated qualifier, Cobra Trading receives from LAMP $0.08 per 100 shares.
